%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Warmind:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:
%^RESET%^ Level 20 Psywarrior
%^RESET%^ 20 Base Intelligence (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
 %^RESET%^L1: flawless control
 %^RESET%^L4: mind over matter
 %^RESET%^L7: battle psyche

Warminds have mastered their awareness of the matter around them. They are completely in tune with their own bodies and can make minute changes to their cells, boosting their performance. This awareness extends to the world around them, helping them to innately understand the physical realm. Warminds are able to flawlessly shape their powers so that they do not harm members of their own parties. They are also able to manipulate their own bodies so that their wounds heal themselves. Because of their dedication to perfecting their own bodies, warminds receive a +2 on all endurance and athletics checks.

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^See also: %^RESET%^feats, skills, spells, cast, prepare